title: Cannot synchronize a .java file and another resource
OB: When attempting to synchronize a .java file and another resource, an error occurs.
EB: Both the .java file and the other resource should be successfully synchronized without any errors.
SR:
1. Open the application.
2. Navigate to the synchronization feature.
3. Select a .java file and another resource to synchronize.
4. Attempt to synchronize the selected files.
5. Observe the error that occurs.
